 Congratulations are in order for Nollywood actress Eucharia Anunobi who just bagged a Doctor of Philosophy (PhD) in Christian Education and Ministerial Acts from the Kingdom Life Bible College and Seminary International. The movie star shared the good news with fans and followers via her Instagram page, attributing her success to her determination to brave the rigours of academics. In the certificate given to Anunobi, the institution said the 56-year-old actress was “found worthy in character and learning”. View this post on Instagram A post shared by Eucharia Anunobi (@euchariaanunobi)